Proud to work with appropriators to secure full funding for the Farm and Ranch Stress Assistance Network to provide mental health resources for farmers in MN & across rural America. They will finally receive the support they deserve! Read my statement:  https://emmer.house.gov/media-center/press-releases/emmer-ensures-full-funding-address-stress-farm-country …

#SCOTUS ruled in favor of the #PeaceCross today. I proudly joined the amicus brief w/ @SteveScalise & @tedcruz. The #PeaceCross will continue to stand as a testament to the religious liberty of all Americans and a reminder of the brave soldiers who sacrificed their lives in #WWI.

Glad to see our partners in Mexico ratify #USMCA.
